divs: sighting details i did a picture of a unknown aircraft. it's happen on jun 24 2011 at 20.53 bulgarian time.i am living at the end fo the east part of dobrich (my place) and i saw it from the balcony of my flat. my wife and my 7 year old son was witnesses. it was a glowing star-like and not so fast moving object. noiseless and without air condense traces. an amasing object ! i did optical zoom of my camera fujifilm s5500 in max (10x). the distance from me and this object was approximately 10 km and 3-4 km altitude, according my account. it float from north to south at east of dobrich. i would like to send you the original picture and few with color filter manipulated ! when i did digital zoom i saw an jet aircraft in plasma cloud with two plasma streams, one from middle to down and one from middle to upper side ! you'll see on the picture ... i think this technology is very advanced, because it use too much energy to create plasma cloud ! probably a copy-paste from the aliens technology ... just amasing ! just amasing ! best regards, [name and email address removed\cms\tg]
